               "98890017/t 800 1500/f Jinx 250": "WizardSong/7 8/farmer -500 -500 0 Jinx 7 7 0/skippable/pause 1000/speak Jinx \"Hmmm...$3#$b#If I just add a bit less onion powder, then it really might work this time!$0#$b#And it will taste at least a little better.$0\"/pause 500/warp farmer 7 13/playSound doorClose/move farmer 0 -4 0/pause 500/faceDirection Jinx 2/emote Jinx 16/pause 500/speak Jinx \"Human!$3#$b#What are you doing in my house uninvited?$5\"/pause 500/emote farmer 28/pause 500/speak Jinx \"...Well, I guess it's fine.$3#$b#If you're going to be my disciple, you'll need access to my home anyways.$0\"/pause 500/emote farmer 56/pause 500/speak Jinx \"Listen, if you want to be my 'friend', I'll need you to do favors for me in return.$0#$b#These favors will involve bringing me ingredients for my potions and spells and then testing said potions and spells.$0\"/pause 500/emote farmer 28/pause 500/speak Jinx \"Don't be such a scaredy cat.$0#$b#The potions and spells will be harmless.$0#$b#Mostly.$0\"/pause 500/speak Jinx \"Okay, you'll probably experience a few undesirable side effects...$3#$b#Such as plants sprouting from within you or unusual purple tumors growing on your head...$3#$b#But that is just par for the course.$0\"/pause 500/jump farmer 5/emote farmer 36/pause 500/speak Jinx \"Eh, you'll come around to the idea eventually.$0#$b#You seem fairly...malleable.$0\"/pause 500/speak Jinx \"Now...what really did you come here for?$3\"/pause 500/emote farmer 56/pause 500/speak Jinx \"To hang out with me?$3#$b#That's weird.$3#$b#Why would you want to do that?$3\"/pause 500/speak Jinx \"Besides, I'm not really someone who 'hangs out' with others.$3\"/pause 500/speak Jinx \"Well, besides Olina.$0#$b#I can always make time to 'hang out' with her.$0\"/pause 500/speak Jinx \"N-no particular reason for that or anything!$3#$b#We're just good friends. That's why.$3\"/pause 500/speak Jinx \"Anyways, I'm going to have to ask you to leave.$0#$b#Your time here may have been short, but I'm quite busy right now.$0#$b#I have no time to be distracted by your strange...human-ness.$0\"/pause 500/speak Jinx \"I suppose you can come back later...$0#$b#As long as you're willing to prove yourself useful to me.$0\"/pause 500/emote farmer 56/pause 500/speak Jinx \"Very good then.$0#$b#Leave this place at once.$0\"/pause 1000/end",

