               "98890072/t 600 2000/f Jinx 2500/e 98890071": "none/7 8/farmer 5 10 0 Jinx 5 8 2 Olina -200 -200 0 Captain -200 -199 0 Lulu -200 -198 0/pause 1000/message \"...It took a while, but you explained everything Olina had shared with you about her memories to Jinx.\"/pause 500/message \"He seems to ponder on it for a moment.\"/pause 500/speak Jinx \"Yes...I remember all of this as well.$2\"/pause 500/speak Jinx \"I'm sure you already figured this out, but I am the Jax person she spoke of.$2\"/pause 500/emote farmer 60/pause 500/speak Jinx \"Judging by your expression, it was fairly obvious to you indeed.$2\"/pause 500/speak Jinx \"Funnily enough, I seem to have regained my memories around the same time as Olina.$2#$b#I guess it's due to us being connected in our past.$2\"/pause 500/speak Jinx \"And the car crash...yes, that is what happened.$2#$b#It was all my fault...$2#$b#The guilt I feel over it sears stronger in my mind than any of my old memories.$2\"/pause 500/emote farmer 28/pause 500/speak Jinx \"You're both probably wondering how the car crash happened in the first place.$2#$b#How could I have been so careless, right?$2\"/pause 500/speak Jinx \"Honestly, there were just a lot of things going on in my life that led up to that horrible accident...$2\"/pause 500/fade/viewport -500 -500/warp farmer -200 -197/warp Jinx -200 -196/warp Lulu 17 15/faceDirection Lulu 3/warp Captain 15 15/faceDirection Captain 1/pause 1000/changeSprite Captain JinxDad/changeSprite Lulu JinxMom/changeSprite Jinx HumanPast/changePortrait Jinx HumanPast/changeName Jinx Jax/changeLocation otohime.AV_JinxHousePast/message \"On the Friday the day before the party...\"/pause 500/fade/viewport 22 15/pause 1000/warp Jinx 27 13/faceDirection Jinx 2/playSound doorClose/pause 200/speak Jinx \"I'm home-$2\"/pause 500/emote Jinx 16/pause 200/faceDirection Jinx 3/pause 1000/emote Jinx 40/pause 500/emote Lulu 12/pause 200/message \"Mom: YOU'RE the root of all of our problems, Tae!\"/message \"Not me!\"/pause 500/emote Captain 12/pause 500/message \"Dad: Are you kidding me?\"/message \"You're so full of it.\"/pause 500/jump Lulu 5/pause 400/message \"Mom: No, are YOU kidding ME?\"/message \"I've been breaking my back bringing in all of the money while you wallow in self-pity over your silly, made-up 'writer's-block'!\"/pause 500/message \"Dad: I can't believe you just said that.\"/message \"No, wait, I actually can because you've ALWAYS been like this.\"/pause 500/faceDirection Captain 3/pause 200/message \"Dad: God, I knew I never should have left Korea.\"/pause 600/jump Lulu 5/pause 400/message \"Mom: I wish you had stayed in Korea too!\"/message \"Lord knows my life would've been a hell of a lot better without you in it!\"/pause 500/emote Jinx 40/pause 500/speak Jinx \"(...They're at it again.)$2#$b#(I should just head to my room and avoid getting dragged into it.)$2\"/pause 500/move Jinx 0 5 3 true/fade/changeName Jinx Jinx/changePortrait Jinx/viewport -500 -500/warp Lulu -200 -195/warp Captain -200 -194/pause 1000/speak Jinx \"My parents got into arguments quite frequently.$2#$b#I was pretty used to it by this point, but it could still shake me up a little sometimes.$2\"/pause 500/speak Jinx \"I always wished I had a normal family instead.$2\"/pause 500/speak Jinx \"...But enough about that.$2\"/pause 500/speak Jinx \"When I got to my room, I remembered that the party Olina and I agreed to go to was the next day.$2#$b#I wasn't too into the idea of going to that party, but I had a sudden realization...$2\"/pause 500/speak Jinx \"The party could be a good time to to tell Olina something.$2#$b#Something that I had been wanting to tell her for a long time...$2\"/pause 500/speak Jinx \"Um, the details of that aren't important!$3\"/pause 500/speak Jinx \"Either way, the party eventually came and about an hour into it I felt a surge of confidence pushing me to tell her.$2\"/pause 500/warp Jinx 21 16/faceDirection Jinx 2/warp Olina 30 26/faceDirection Olina 1/warp Captain 31 26/faceDirection Captain 3/pause 1000/changeSprite Captain Chad/changeSprite Jinx HumanPast/changeSprite Olina HumanPast/changePortrait Jinx HumanPast/changePortrait Olina HumanPast/changeLocation otohime.AV_PartyHouse/changeName Jinx Jax/fade/viewport 21 28/pause 1000/speed Jinx 5/move Jinx 0 8 2/pause 200/textAboveHead Jinx \"Olina!\"/pause 1500/move Jinx 0 2 1/pause 100/speak Jinx \"Hey, 'Lina-\"/pause 500/emote Jinx 16/pause 1000/emote Olina 56/pause 500/textAboveHead Olina \"Hehe~ You're so funny!\"/pause 2500/emote Captain 56/pause 500/speak Jinx \"....$2\"/pause 1000/message \"I had lost all confidence.\"/pause 500/faceDirection Jinx 2/pause 500/message \"In that moment, all I could notice were the drinks on the table in front of me.\"/pause 500/emote Jinx 40/pause 500/speak Jinx \"I know I shouldn't...$2\"/pause 500/speak Jinx \"But...ugh.$2#$b#Anything to take the edge off.$2\"/pause 500/move Jinx 0 4 2 true/fade/viewport -500 -500/pause 1000/changeName Jinx Jinx/changePortrait Jinx/changeSprite Jinx/warp Jinx 5 8/faceDirection Jinx 2/warp farmer 5 10/faceDirection farmer 0/warp Olina -200 -193/warp Captain -200 -192/changeLocation otohime.AV_JinxHouse/viewport 7 8/pause 1000/speak Jinx \"I still hate myself for that decision.$2#$b#It cost the life of the person I cared about the most.$2\"/pause 500/emote farmer 28/pause 500/speak Jinx \"Now what am I going to do...$2#$b#I have to tell her that I'm Jax, don't I?$2\"/pause 500/emote farmer 40/pause 500/speak Jinx \"...Your face says it all.$2\"/pause 500/speak Jinx \"Alright...It's the right thing to do.$2\"/pause 500/speak Jinx \"I'll go tell her now.$2#$b#But...would you mind coming with me?$3#$b#Your presence will make me feel a bit better.$2\"/pause 500/emote farmer 32/pause 500/speak Jinx \"Thank you, @.$2\"/pause 500/end"

